id=pdh_qqd
name=PDH Staging Daemon
version=v1.1
versionCode=2
author=ChainlessChain
description=Stages app data for ChainlessChain on-device collection (QQ nt_msg.db + uids / WeChat EnMicroMsg.db + uin/IMEI / any app's plaintext dbs), working around MIUI/HyperOS app-process cross-app-read restriction. Root daemon, non-app context.
